{"obj_edit_time":"1710151715","blocks":[{"block_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh","block_type":1,"children":["AodBdljHXoEykBxtV95cddL2n6f","DxWUdNsUdoBSNCxGrOscCHKLndv","VOZkd0TIUoojuIxnIxrcNxrencg","VGJgdY9T9oYnuAxI4aSctASBnjf","DfS3dgMQWoWIHXxAmhCckyE6nZe","BLnxdPFl7o92CIx1dtJcfxi2nng","VLoTdPAkqo2ckqxo2CAc0w4Ingd","M7szdv9TkoucOSxnB7bcYZQFnEH","P25ydV0pPoQYJoxwufWcwUDsnue","KfAzdZUxSos7y0xf9trc1MsFnVh","ANEEdwOmlopAXkxUOAkcYZ5jn1b","ILZgduYEio8rm1xhivXcI3l2nJd","Sjw3d4pRXorYo1xjIfmcJP6Ynxb"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"業務介紹","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"AodBdljHXoEykBxtV95cddL2n6f","block_type":4,"heading2":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"DxWUdNsUdoBSNCxGrOscCHKLndv","block_type":2,"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"證券後台KYC審核是指證券公司在進行客戶管理和交易監管過程中，對客戶身份和風險進行核實和評估的業務流程。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"VOZkd0TIUoojuIxnIxrcNxrencg","block_type":2,"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"VGJgdY9T9oYnuAxI4aSctASBnjf","block_type":4,"heading2":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"KYC ","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}},{"text_run":{"content":"步驟","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"DfS3dgMQWoWIHXxAmhCckyE6nZe","block_type":2,"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"券商在後台審核客戶提交的開戶申請時，通常會進行以下壹系列的操作和流程，以確保申請的合規性和准確性。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"BLnxdPFl7o92CIx1dtJcfxi2nng","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"申請接收與初步篩查：券商後台接收客戶提交的開戶申請，並對申請進行初步篩查。這包括檢查申請表的完整性、必填字段的准確性和必要文件的附帶情況。如果申請不完整或存在問題，可能會要求客戶補充提供所需的信息或文件。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"VLoTdPAkqo2ckqxo2CAc0w4Ingd","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"身份驗證：券商會對客戶提交的身份證明文件進行驗證。這可以通過與公共數據庫或第三方身份驗證服務進行比對來完成。目的是確保客戶提供的身份信息是真實有效的，並與申請表中的信息一致。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"M7szdv9TkoucOSxnB7bcYZQFnEH","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"風險評估：券商會對客戶的風險承受能力進行評估。這通常涉及對客戶的財務狀況、投資經驗、投資目標和風險偏好等方面進行分析和評估。根據評估結果，券商可以確定適合客戶的投資産品和服務。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"P25ydV0pPoQYJoxwufWcwUDsnue","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"資金來源調查：券商會對客戶申請中提供的資金來源進行調查。這包括核實客戶的收入來源、資産情況和可能的資金流動路徑。目的是確保客戶的資金來源合法合規，以防止洗錢和其他非法資金活動。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"KfAzdZUxSos7y0xf9trc1MsFnVh","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"反洗錢和反恐融資監測：券商會通過後台系統進行反洗錢和反恐怖融資監測，以識別和報告任何可疑的交易活動。這可以通過使用自動化系統和風險警示工具來實現，以便及時發現潛在的違規行爲。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"ANEEdwOmlopAXkxUOAkcYZ5jn1b","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"審核和批准：在完成上述審核步驟後，券商會對開戶申請進行最終審核，並根據審核結果做出批准或拒絕的決定。如果開戶申請符合公司的要求和法律法規的規定，券商將批准申請，並進行後續的開戶流程。如果存在問題或風險，可能會拒絕開戶申請或要求進壹步核實和調查。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh"},{"block_id":"ILZgduYEio8rm1xhivXcI3l2nJd","block_type":2,"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"Sjw3d4pRXorYo1xjIfmcJP6Ynxb","block_type":2,"parent_id":"HR8td2q3koeem9xU3GHcV8EmnSh","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}